description.en:
Epcoin is a social media site where social interactions carry real economic value. When you post a photo and someone gives it a 'like', you receive a micro-transaction of the epcoin. When you 'like' someone else's post, you're giving them a micro-tip as well. Epcoin works like any other social media site; users comment, post photos, follow others, and browse feeds, all while earning real money for posting good content.

Money is transferred using a cryptotoken called EPCOIN . Once you earn money, you can withdraw it on listed Exchanger wallet.
